{"hash":"cd527726235043440cff51096c025a42f405c651","data":{"tag":{"title":"javascript","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"극단적(?)으로 가벼운 Moon 프론트엔드 프레임워크를 소개합니다.","path":"/4/","date":"2020. 09. 06","timeToRead":5,"description":"가볍고 빠름을 장점으로 내세운 javascript 기반 프론트엔드 프레임워크(frontend framework).","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>요약 : 이런게 있구나 정도.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>현재 구독중인 Medium 에서 관심이 갈만한 프레임워크가 소개되었습니다. \"Moon\"이라 불리는 프레임워크인데요.\n프론트엔트 라이브러리이므로 Vue, React등과 비교됩니다. 제가 본 원글은 아래 링크를 통해 들어가실 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.bitsrc.io/introduction-to-moon-js-c1526fcb543e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">blog.bitsrc.io introduction to Moon</a></p>\n<p>라이브러리 공식사이트는 <a href=\"https://moonjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://moonjs.org/</a> 입니다. 링크를 들어가보면 메인화면 아랫쪽에 눈에 띌만한\n그래프가 보입니다.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 998 298' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-1c2f4796ffcdd0ce2d8679bf5f1d6901'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-1c2f4796ffcdd0ce2d8679bf5f1d6901)' width='998' height='298' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAATCAYAAAAgcwuHAAAACXBIWXMAAA9hAAAPYQGoP6dpAAAF0UlEQVRYw71Ya2xTZRjuaHt6Lu0uvZxzejm97bRdu63rVjbGRrltQjCg8QJoiKKQAIkGjRkkQDQCMQb0B4oxTGMiaoyJQoxT5w%2bFETEx%2bMvEyB9/GFB%%2buIpGzAtAZQuUn0c3JdHsAhjsGAEdfiMrs%2bA37kZEh8ppkMtJshAm7SpBJTvsqB1oD7ZC33ZeoQW3wUhlocUaDVd/GzSg%2bHF25cZ8mcqmB0BzeA%2bPgQrLdx2/SPYbpyi6xHwjz8ASWAEpKcnoDRZF5mIh9LANAVUYrE%2bDO7Yadi%2b%2bxP2s5fAjV2C7cIfENY%2bAqmBco5kzKsTJiRWMSGzYJJvJg9S50rAJ4dp0aOw3ToF2%2b3TBhn8tgfHFVADAUz%2bqa5ViLX1wx3OQiivySz8RIAzBPv738B6FbD%2bNB6/AcJ9uyDV%2beAiE1K8Gfjc9J4jAqlRn0ihGRbD8NP51QimeqZNAbFyXlMIOD03AhhgkByY5aA3mpuqAEaASwN3cgzWXwDbjzcpbsF6mQi4exuENQUIz%2b%2bE79AT8FLwzIT6C6YmVA0/1kYpQLtvpgAzE5ZYufTPAwHlRsTcWI6ZTMAgIATunXOw/koEXLxthPUKETDwKLh3h8h4zpEBjRhhZSa0Z6uhhEoTMldAApnuAWMTyhUgykxB48E%2b%2bxJwsu8oDEOWk0UTnA8C2OjWsuMmyO6lJybgJ6NzauYEDG6FY3g3gX5BBkQmdJOZ0Kfgn9piOoFqBLR2D0Jr6TUI4GmhEqs0CvOQpBHsWghl4U73QcsPQu1YSSbcRSpLEAGH5kZA%2beKLCmg3JOiQo2RmUXo5DkGNgadRcgXBvX0WtktEwA/XKW7AdrmoAEaAjRHAXJhFjQSU8FkXyIj3kgmX%2bgBPOAc9twqq3kPPkIqaaKeHR8F9exXcmZ/hIBO2n78CseceOD7YR5ij41WA4Y9AqLUKGI0QSV9NdBcbIfKAxqYCGdo6ZDJbENbuhcezFk4yOeuHF1D3F7CIfGARKaHub8CxZhvs7w2R9M9TfE6pMErjGDhKAZF1ZKwiTGOEIqnNHWbVJ09luA3%2beC8Gbd9jsxXYyP2LTfZbuN9%2bDYo4AMtXF1H3D%2bGS%2bdb9TnEN4Fc8BNvIc4T5dRn%2bWXA7NlEKTsU3JaCearlCBthEKRAiJ%2b6M7EUhdgxLI0exRDuC3shLiEUGIG/fA//ht6AcOA55/3EoB9%2bAf%2bkGqI9thHJ8L9SXn4F89GnIrwzBv2EDGmXq0ZXUjM1QUXl5ow%2bJpPsJ80UMRE%2biEDqBQnAYBe0EotEB%2bHbuR%2bDgm1D2vQqF4T/7Ovzd66DueBjKa2X4x4YQWLsODT4yWKXGTrD8MMIpGsLZHHIrViLWSb15QIMzwHruEMI09nWvRoveRaXPDxflq6tBRz0ZXmuiD3p4MSS7Bhe1qNIMB5vKw1DpMGZXAoh2daB9eT8inVlwfhUuhi8GEdda0ZtfaeBLAt1n71AlaBBiaEv2o1nLQ2T43pQpfm3HYdo50ZeGk3LPqbBOrygjVncFVhFY90chkjkW63GLkWtGvgUzxesaj7bm%2bIThK2JPxs9U4GdmjW%2bZ7Zn6/96vtSW%2bU/iWuUxmpj8v5vsfnYXE/w8%2bLurHOiu%2bzAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"998\" alt=\"번들크기 및 속도 비교그래프\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/size_speed.82a2fbd.d7be5ddf677a535a8f3f0375cc92fcf3.png 480w, /assets/static/size_speed.d4ea800.d7be5ddf677a535a8f3f0375cc92fcf3.png 998w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/size_speed.d4ea800.d7be5ddf677a535a8f3f0375cc92fcf3.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/size_speed.d4ea800.d7be5ddf677a535a8f3f0375cc92fcf3.png\" width=\"998\" alt=\"번들크기 및 속도 비교그래프\"></noscript>\n<span class=\"img-title\">번들크기 및 속도 비교그래프</span></p>\n<p>원래 자기들이 만든 프레임워크가 가장 좋다고 하는 법이지만 실제 CLI를 생성하는 기본 템플릿 프로젝트를 빌드한 결과를 비교하면 용량차이가 어느정도 나는 건 사실이긴 합니다 😅</p>\n<p>그럼 체험을 위해 직접 Moon을 설치하고, 기본템플릿을 통해 SPA를 생성해보겠습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-moon-cli-설치-및-프로젝트-생성\"><a href=\"#1-moon-cli-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EB%B0%8F-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. Moon CLI 설치 및 프로젝트 생성</h2>\n<p>cmd 에서 아래와 같이 명령어를 입력하세요.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g moon-cli\nmoon create {생성할 프로젝트명}</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"2-패키지-설치\"><a href=\"#2-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. 패키지 설치</h2>\n<p>생성한 프로젝트 폴더로 이동한 뒤 <code>npm install</code> 명령을 입력하세요.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-cross-env-설치\"><a href=\"#3-cross-env-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>3. cross-env 설치</h2>\n<p>여러 개발환경에서도 NODE_ENV 를 제대로 사용할 수 있도록 cross-env를 설치해주세요.\n개발자가 실수한 것인지 용량을 극단적(?)으로 줄여보고 싶었던건진 알 수 없지만, 해당작업이 없으면 Windows 환경에선 npm 명령이 오류납니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev cross-env</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"4-packagejson-편집\"><a href=\"#4-packagejson-%ED%8E%B8%EC%A7%91\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>4. package.json 편집</h2>\n<p>npm 명령어가 정상적으로 동작할 수 있도록 아래 두 명령어 <code>dev</code>와 <code>build</code>를 변경하세요.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&quot;dev&quot;: &quot;cross-env NODE_ENV=development webpack-dev-server --config webpack.config.js&quot;,\n&quot;build&quot;: &quot;cross-env NODE_ENV=production webpack --config webpack.config.js&quot;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"5-실행\"><a href=\"#5-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>5. 실행</h2>\n<p>생성한 프로젝트 폴더로 이동한 뒤 <code>npm run dev</code> 명령을 입력하세요. 정상적으로 동작한다면\nwebpack 개발서버 실행과 함께 결과물이 브라우저에 띄워집니다.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1280 1040' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-349b59a3148cb5b3f13e4ef717443afe'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-349b59a3148cb5b3f13e4ef717443afe)' width='1280' height='1040' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA0CAYAAAA62j4JAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAEm0lEQVRo3u2Z7U9bVRzH78v9E2riW01cpUBbaHv7fNtLH2EdGqfxxSIZlAEdqEu2hde8MfEVEp1uYBRINNN3cxp8YcAFyBA3I9ChkuKm0EdasL39es7pg6AzmmghtOck3/xOzzm99/v73HPOvbcVztgv4ZSjC0FbN4J2Ikc3AuZX0G4%2bhw5L9z714JTtHLpcb%2bBi4GNccH%2bIQc8U0SQG3VWWZ18s6UKpbajswTP9h5/K%2bKniGO8UXvVPszj8wg3ifRKXOj/C64FpCF7LS7C5jPB6vUQyfO1uiKZWNGpUaNI2oEnzLDQ6Nau3iGqctvbjNXKwkHQVffJ19BMNuCcORf1t40wD8jjCzuLnkOsdFnult4mXa%2bglfeeJBkjbedc11tfH4nX0Ot9DyHmVtYW9Ewh7JiDodWa0tpCE1Y3QanQsiqIJer0BBr0RJpMZKhWB0KxFg1oN0WCB3STD2GJBq8aE5oYWnHxaTdRYVT3zlBqNKi2aVDpoW41QeYi/Zis6rWdh0Fnh6egmXtsQMIiQW83QNouQrG3Mp2R1wyJKCHiC6OsOM980b1HngOCUZEhOCQ6HAy6Xi0WfzwdZltmsCAQCMBqNsNlssJO%2b9o52BIMdcHvc5LMNJrMIrbYZWp2mqtKQcxiMeohGA8wSgd9pgsPmwMv%%2bFtcEcD2ZgE9T4LMgJ/QIHwF/2M38XAzwcYpSqF2AbBZkKdRQXRFwfgg8O7gLqLfK6U%2b5VC9HMEmWPjXY6rp50gA5PN5FmdmZjA6Oopbtz7H1i8xPHzwK37efIDoZhSxWKw2ZsCfn%2byocjm2A2JsbAw6nQ6hUAgjIyMYHh7G5ctXEA6HMTk5WdoIcwe%2bWy1/VZ0Bf3e8jY0NLC4sYPnbZczNzWJpaQmzs7NYXV1FNBp91JGq5q3qM0BRFKRTaSSTKWSzWWxvb2NvbxcZUkf5gVApbn50iWQz9D/INBsXj8fY/3rHcgZUAJCkflhfxwK54pHIKrvaa2srWLyziJV7ESzMkDrRd8truHt3GfO3b2N1LYKv5%2bbILJnH/cj90kNzoXaWwP5Sfhv8x%2beH474J0qXwqHggyX2i/fvH/N/vCEdyF/gvOpZ3Af6LEAfAAXAAHAAHwAFwABwAB8ABHB8A9aQKgL3dHOq10NyFZCzLKpRGPYnmTHP/HQmJfP4m2%2bsDAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"1280\" alt=\"실행결과\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/helloworld.82a2fbd.ceafdbffb707459007eda9366bfc4657.png 480w, /assets/static/helloworld.7c86909.ceafdbffb707459007eda9366bfc4657.png 1280w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/helloworld.7c86909.ceafdbffb707459007eda9366bfc4657.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/helloworld.7c86909.ceafdbffb707459007eda9366bfc4657.png\" width=\"1280\" alt=\"실행결과\"></noscript>\n<span class=\"img-title\">실행결과</span></p>\n<p>이대로 끝내기엔 아쉬우니 버튼 이벤트 정도하나만 추가해보겠습니다. 😅</p>\n<h2 id=\"6-srcviewhomejs-에-버튼추가\"><a href=\"#6-srcviewhomejs-%EC%97%90-%EB%B2%84%ED%8A%BC%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>6. src/view/home.js 에 버튼추가</h2>\n<p>실행을 종료시켜 주시고, 기본 생성된 프로젝트에서 src/view/home.js 로 이동해주세요. 1.0.0-beta.7 버전기준으로\n아래와 같은 내용이 나올 것입니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Moon</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"moon\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> moonLogo <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"images/moon-logo.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> div<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Moon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">m</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> data <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a-x-c a-y-l-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-x-c m-y-3\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>moonLogo alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Moon logo\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-15 s-y-15\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-t-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-t-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Jump</span> into the <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://moonjs.org/guide\"</span> target<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"_blank\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>guide<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span> to <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> started<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre>\n<p>위 소스를 아래와 같이 바꿔주세요.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Moon</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"moon\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> moonLogo <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"images/moon-logo.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> div<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> button <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Moon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">m</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// button 추가</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> data <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a-x-c a-y-l-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-x-c m-y-3\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>moonLogo alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Moon logo\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-15 s-y-15\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-t-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-t-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Jump</span> into the <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://moonjs.org/guide\"</span> target<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"_blank\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>guide<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span> to <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> started<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\\\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>hello<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"7-호출할-이벤트-함수-생성\"><a href=\"#7-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C%ED%95%A0-%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%A4%ED%8A%B8-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>7. 호출할 이벤트 함수 생성</h2>\n<p>소스 코드 맨 아래에 호출할 <code>function</code> 을 생성해주세요. 예시로 <code>alert</code>을 호출하는 <code>sayHello</code> 함수를 추가해보겠습니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Moon</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"moon\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> moonLogo <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"images/moon-logo.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> div<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> button <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Moon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">m</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// button 추가</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> data <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a-x-c a-y-l-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-x-c m-y-3\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>moonLogo alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Moon logo\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-15 s-y-15\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-t-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"s-x-25 a-t-c\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Jump</span> into the <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://moonjs.org/guide\"</span> target<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"_blank\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>guide<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span> to <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> started<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\\\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>hello<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">sayHello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello \"</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// main.js에서 넘어온 data를 바인딩</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<p>이제 실행해볼까요?</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1246 927' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-f2a486c5de49ca3f2fe284f420ca5630'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-f2a486c5de49ca3f2fe284f420ca5630)' width='1246' height='927' xlink:href='data:image/gif%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAwCAYAAAChS3wfAAAACXBIWXMAAAPoAAAD6AG1e1JrAAACVElEQVRo3u2YzWsTQRjG56KCXv0LPHrxJqIQ9CLqtRYvCoJ/gUexB3tSUQ9Ri1jB2ybUS9tQL%2boxtSHZJrJJpHaTEBI9tAHbRJLNZnb2cbObrY0hUJF8Td%2bB2Rl2Zj%2be3z7vzOwwHPLECAABIAAEgAAQAAJAAAgAASAABIAAEIDBJ9u220e3LoQNy7I757w2vy4lgP1ChfUHhA9jFBBG4gBf33YRyK42YBpWDwRpHSBcrTY%2bzgPXj2/jHPuAqTNv8b1Q7YIgJQBfXKUscPOEjQCL4/yRME6yu5i59cltsywhrwO8uAdy6wJTzpMvH4sicDSCU%2bw%2bbgcU%2bccAXxhvCdw7C1xiFVxgUZxmESjBpOcALqkDfFFtiztewFbRwqs7wMzFBiIval4fdE%2bJ0jqgT2vPVCkVACGEW%2bq6jthaDGpCdULBm/7MJu%2b4w5JnGvx7deeLW1xcwtUr13BjehpzL%2bfw6OFjBIPP8fTJM8w%2bmIVhGF3XDdoRbBji9zsgny9g/vUbvFtYQEgJIRwKQ1EULC8t4/3KCur1eo/gQTqCDTPeDyrE/1%2bQwgG5jW/Qkl%2bw6ZRf02loWhap9TiymQ3o2R9QP%2behqToKuTyS8QQy6QwSaypSagqx6Cp2dqqTDaDVajmDnAmj0XDr7cw5d2K9iXJxC5uZMn5Was4YwVHd3d3rb5pObjb3QmeiABz0hUulErRUGrXar/%2b%2b11gPgv0y55bzxXlncdS//0Q64F8dMuyNkBHvCGGoX3ksHTAuiQAQAAJAAAgAASAABIAAEAACQAAOZfoNYmyJ5%2bJIisIAAAAASUVORK5CYII=' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"1246\" alt=\"실행결과\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/hello_moon.82a2fbd.7b941cf9c0c58343644ecf1398bbd88e.gif 480w, /assets/static/hello_moon.3124ec6.7b941cf9c0c58343644ecf1398bbd88e.gif 1246w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1246px) 100vw, 1246px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/hello_moon.3124ec6.7b941cf9c0c58343644ecf1398bbd88e.gif\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/hello_moon.3124ec6.7b941cf9c0c58343644ecf1398bbd88e.gif\" width=\"1246\" alt=\"실행결과\"></noscript>\n<span class=\"img-title\">실행결과</span></p>\n<p>이것으로 Moon 프레임워크를 체험해보았습니다. 아직 Lint 지원이나 서드파티 프레임워크등이 없기 때문에 실제 프로젝트에 도입하기엔 아직 무리가 있겠지만\n분명 매력적인 프레임워크이긴 합니다. 🙂</p>\n<p>저도 시간이 된다면 Moon 프레임워크 기반으로 간략한 토이 프로젝트를 진행해봐야겠습니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>NOTE : 예제 소스는 <a href=\"https://github.com/ddochea0314/hello-moon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/ddochea0314/hello-moon</a> 에 올렸습니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"}},{"node":{"title":"Vuetify Treeview를 대시보드 형식의 Layout에 사용하려 할때 겪었던 문제 🖖","path":"/3/","date":"2020. 09. 02","timeToRead":2,"description":"css의 flex, grid로 만든 Layout에 적용할때 안되던 삽질을 까먹지 않고자 작성한 글입니다.","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>요약 : Treeview를 가변적인 크기의 특정 영역안에서 사용하고싶다면, 부모영역의 높이, 너비가 %만 존재하면 안된다. 부모노드 중 최소 한곳에서 vw, vh 사용할 것.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>현재 사내에서 사용할 웹 기반 솔루션을 개발하고 있습니다. 개발초기라 본격적인 구현에 앞서 UI 레이아웃을 잡고 그 위에 Vuetify 기반의 컨트롤을 배치하고 있었습니다.\n대략 아래와 같은 디자인으로 구성하려했죠.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1280 1040' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-355117976feb481e4bc55afbf3064b0f'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/fi